eplyTime":"2019-06-03T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"一定係黃大仙現崇山  一個字「屋苑」"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"屋苑死忠出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請解釋屋苑點解一定好過單幢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"地鐵站上蓋係好好喎 多數都好乾淨企理 仲大型會所同平台 <br />\n<br />\n單棟我真係諗唔到有咩好 尤其唔係港島區個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T19:08:48.000Z","msg":"首先 <br />\n屋苑不等於地鐵上蓋 屋苑定單幢同位置無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把屋苑個位閪到爆 <br />\n荃灣中心 荃景花園 麗晶花園 海濱花園 美景花園 偉恒昌 翔龍灣 河畔花園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無車住呢堆屋苑<br />\n出入慘過食屎<br />\n<br />\n第二 <br />\n乾淨企理係睇你會法團班人有冇貪污<br />\n管理公司有冇古惑<br />\n唔關屋苑定唔屋苑事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日出康城係大屋苑新樓啦 但出哂名管到pat屎咁<br />\n黃埔花園又係出哂名差<br />\n九龍灣德寶個外牆同平台又舊又殘十足粵語殘片feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未計大屋企全部比黑社會圍標或者管理公司屈你管理費<br />\n住屋苑就真係港九新界無得避玉皇大帝救你唔到比人圍鳩硬標呃鳩硬錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n得近十幾年起既樓先會所 <br />\n唔係個個屋苑都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n很閒用下個腦 唔好人講乜你信乜"},{"pid":"95aa6901f7e26aed7f22e2e07408d8bd283fa476","tid":1183741,"uid":41923,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"899ccdd247e54ef78eda7ea1dd1b953c0157da27","tid":1183741,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8733290e97d12fb8a14fba6e21cfb9265c961ff9","tid":1183741,"uid":41923,"like":2,"dislike"